WEBVTT

00:02:59.107 --> 00:03:01.313
Na rais aliposimama kuhutubu,


00:03:01.313 --> 00:03:05.920
Nilijipata nimesimama nimkemea,


00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:09.114
nikimwambia awakumbuke waasiriwa 
wa ghasia za baada ya uchaguzi,


00:03:09.114 --> 00:03:11.390
kumaliza ufisadi.


00:03:11.390 --> 00:03:13.595
Na punde si punde,


00:03:13.595 --> 00:03:16.707
polisi walinirukia kama simba wenye njaa.


00:03:16.707 --> 00:03:18.564
Walinifunga mdomo


00:03:18.564 --> 00:03:20.491
na kuniburuta hadi nje ya uwanja,


00:03:20.491 --> 00:03:23.462
ambapo walinitwanga na kunitupa jela.


00:03:25.112 --> 00:03:31.870
Usiku huo nililala kwenye sakafu baridi
ndani ya jela,
